{
"#name"
:
{
"claw"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"x-cmd AI 消息机器人"
,
"en"
:
"x-cmd AI message bot"
}
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
{
"x claw <SUBCMD>"
:
null
}
]
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"把你的 AI（Claude、Kimi、Codex 等）接入微信、飞书、Telegram。\n在群里 @机器人即可对话，AI 会自主查资料、写代码、处理数据，并把结果发回群里。\n直接输入 x claw 即可和 AI 管理员对话，管理所有平台、查看聊天记录、设置定时任务。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Connect your AI (Claude, Kimi, Codex, etc.) to WeChat, Feishu, Telegram.\nMention the bot in a group chat and the AI will search, code, and process data autonomously, sending results back.\nJust type x claw to talk to the AI admin — manage platforms, browse chat history, and set up scheduled tasks.\n"
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"直接输入 x claw，和 AI 管理员对话，管理所有 IM 平台、查看聊天记录、设置定时任务。\nx claw start 启动后台服务，机器人开始在群里接收和回复消息。\nx claw 'msg' 单条处理，不用进交互模式也能快速查询或执行一次性任务。\n"
,
"en"
:
"Type x claw to talk to the AI admin — manage IM platforms, browse chat history, and set up scheduled tasks.\nx claw start starts the background service so the bot begins receiving and replying in groups.\nx claw 'msg' for quick queries or one-off tasks without entering interactive mode.\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 直接和 AI 管理者对话"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Talk to the AI admin"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw start"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 启动机器人，开始在群里接收消息"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Start the bot to begin receiving messages in groups"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x claw '今天飞书群有什么重要消息'"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 单条查询聊天记录，快速获取摘要"
,
"en"
:
"Example: Quick chat history query for a summary"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:Admin"
:
[
"manager"
]
,
"#subcmd:Service"
:
[
"start"
,
"stop"
,
"restart"
,
"status"
,
"log"
,
"connect"
,
"disconnect"
]
,
"#subcmd:Platform"
:
[
"weixin"
,
"telegram"
,
"feishu"
,
"qywx"
]
,
"#subcmd:Task"
:
[
"cron"
]
,
"#subcmd:inner"
:
[
"agentrequest"
]
,
"start"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"启动 x claw 后台服务，让机器人开始在 IM 群里接收和回复消息"
,
"en"
:
"Start the x claw background service so the bot begins receiving and replying in IM groups"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/start.jso"
}
,
"stop"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"停止 x claw 后台服务，机器人停止接收和回复消息"
,
"en"
:
"Stop the x claw background service, bot stops receiving and replying"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/stop.jso"
}
,
"restart"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"重启 x claw 后台服务，重新连接 IM 平台"
,
"en"
:
"Restart the x claw background service and reconnect IM platforms"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/restart.jso"
}
,
"status"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看网关服务状态"
,
"en"
:
"Show gateway service status"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/status.jso"
}
,
"log"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"查看网关服务日志（按时间线排序）"
,
"en"
:
"Show gateway service log (sorted by timeline)"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/log.jso"
}
,
"connect"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"连接指定 IM 平台及会话，激活消息监听通道。支持同时连接多个平台。"
,
"en"
:
"Connect to IM platform(s) and activate message listener channel. Supports multiple platforms at once."
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/connect.jso"
}
,
"disconnect"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"断开指定 IM 平台及会话的连接，停止对应的消息监听。支持同时断开多个平台。"
,
"en"
:
"Disconnect from IM platform(s) and stop the message listener. Supports multiple platforms at once."
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/disconnect.jso"
}
,
"agentrequest"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"向 AI Agent 发送消息请求，触发 Agent 执行指定任务并将结果回复到对应 IM 会话。"
,
"en"
:
"Send a message request to the AI Agent, triggering it to execute a task and reply to the specified IM session."
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/agentrequest.jso"
}
,
"weixin"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"微信消息查询工具"
,
"en"
:
"WeChat message query tools"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/weixin.jso"
}
,
"telegram"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"Telegram 消息查询工具"
,
"en"
:
"Telegram message query tools"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/telegram.jso"
}
,
"feishu"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"飞书消息查询工具"
,
"en"
:
"Feishu message query tools"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/feishu.jso"
}
,
"cron"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"定时任务管理（封装 x cron）"
,
"en"
:
"Scheduled task management (wraps x cron)"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/cron.jso"
}
,
"manager"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"x claw 的默认子命令。与 AI 管理者对话，管理所有 IM 平台、查看聊天记录、设置定时任务。"
,
"en"
:
"Default subcommand of x claw. Talk to the AI admin to manage IM platforms, browse chat history, and set up scheduled tasks."
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/manager.jso"
}
,
"qywx"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"企业微信消息查询工具"
,
"en"
:
"Qywx message query tools"
}
,
"$ref"
:
"x-advise://claw/data/qywx.jso"
}
}

